<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">
            <li>In the <span class="Emphasis">Privacy</span> tab, click <span class="Emphasis">Add a user or group</span>. </li>
            <li>
                <p>In the Add a User or Group dialog, do the following:</p>
                <ol class="LowerRoman">
                    <li>In the entry field, type the user or group name to add. This populates the list with matching items from the Pulse database. </li>
                    <li>Place a check mark in the box next to the desired user account or group name.</li>
                    <li>Repeat these steps until you have added all of the desired users and groups. </li>
                </ol>
            </li>
            <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">Add</span>. </li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>